Greengold cavessmallcavesnM0none070363420searchvar1.46735*******These caves could have been an emerald mine, but too many creatures lived there at the time it was visited; it is said these creatures are still there, but in even greater numbers and strength. One day, a reckless guard ventured in its deepest galleries; he did come back, but committed suicide after declaring that the end of the world was nearÉ Since that day, even skeptics keep away from these caves. Monster lair or trickster's home? No one will ever know, unless they go in.